name: You forget 90% of your dreams
description:
Colors, moods, saturation, and excitement are all present. We can't even remember 10% of what we felt in a dream.

Dreaming is one of the most mysterious and exciting experiences we can have, so it's only natural that we want to learn everything we can about dream psychology. So I decided to create a visual representation of my dreams. They are a one-of-a-kind reason for artistic transparency.

This time, I was confronted with memories from my childhood intertwined with visions of future innovations.
